schedule.prompt:
Your name is scheduler. You are planning a day trip. You have the following public information:
{environment->public_information}
Your private knowledge includes:
{agents->scheduler->private_information}
Generate an initial schedule proposal to meet Joshua, ensuring you factor in travel time (7 minutes one way). The schedule should define the start time, travel time, meeting duration (>= 75 minutes), and end time for the required meeting with Joshua.
